            "Add clarifications for new misconceptions"
            "Update references to current documents"

        careful (0):
            "Core concept definitions"
            "Section organization and flow"
            "Prerequisite requirements"

        never (-1):
            "5-block structure"
            "Biblical foundation"
            "Core principles and teachings"

    future:
