            "[Expansion of topic coverage]"

        considered (0):
            "[Potential addition - why uncertain]"

        rejected (-1):
            "[Topic explicitly out of scope - why it won't be added]"

synthesis of this document:

    overview:
        see "METADATA exists to" for "purpose, teachings, and philosophy"

    architecture:
        see "CONTENT structure organized as" for "concept ladder and reading flow"

    updates:
        see "CONTENT implementation teachings" for "surgical update points"

